You can share files between pc 

Go to “Network sharing center“

From upper left portion of screen select “change advanced sharing settings“.

Under “File and printer sharing” select “Turn on file and printer sharing” option.

Then click on “Save Changes“.

To allow the two connected systems to view or edit shared data, a folder first needs to be selected and then click on the share tab then select the recipients then click on done.

Now on the second system open file explorer, select the system who is sharing the file, enter the password if password protected.
 
View the contents of the shared folder or edit them.
